project, said designers will meet with memorial supporters ``to get
a feel for what they think it should look like.''
   The designers will then draft plans to present to the memorial's
foundation by early next year. If approved, the design will be
presented to the three agencies for their approval. Purnell
estimated the project would be completed in about 2{ years.
   Private donations are expected to pay for the project, estimated
at $4 million.
