<HEAD>Kinney Named Bureau Chief in West Virginia</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Terry Kinney, assistant chief of bureau for The
Associated Press in Columbus, Ohio, has been named AP's chief of
